What is Threat ?
ﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂﬂ
     Threat is a shoot em' up game in which you control a security
force soldier. With your friends you must save the human colonists
from attack of creatures.

     Threat is Fragment's first game and it took us nearly a year
to make Threat. ( Don't ask why... )

